title: Bacon-Wrapped Pork Roast and Honey-Mustard Gravy with Garlic Smashed Potatoes and Roasted Root Veggies
description: This harvest dinner celebrates all the best flavours of the season: warm root veggies, brined bacon-wrapped pork and roasted garlic smashed potatoes, all covered with a  savoury honey-mustard gravy.
